Package: swisstrace
Title: Correction and Calibration of Swisstrace Twilite Blood Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Granville", "Matheson", email = "mathesong@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Corrects and calibrates raw Swisstrace twilite automatic
    blood-sampling '.crv' files into whole-blood radioactivity input
    functions via background subtraction, decay correction, calibration
    and resampling. Provides per-study calibration lookup by date, a QC
    plot, and BIDS PET blood output.
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
